node.text: My friends and I are Co Owners of this delicious rum. Us all being musicians it’s only right that we put together the official jingle for @selvareyrum .This was fun! Enjoy #TropicalLuxury wherever you are. Cheers to the Family 🍹 🍹 @jamesfauntleroyii  @anderson._paak & @dmile85 Good vibes only all summer long!
